But it requires profound study to become acquainted with all the secrets of our
sea, and with its ebb and flow. ... The whole knowledge of our Art consists in
the discovery of this our sea; any Alchemist who is ignorant of it. is simply
wasting his money. Our sea is derived from the mountain.
